posts.title: I'm a Trump supporter from Romania. WE HAVE THE GREATEST POLITICAL BATTLE OF OUR TIME IN FRONT OF US WITHIN DAYS! I AM BEGGING YOU, SEND PRAYERS, HIGH ENERGY AND ANY KIND OF SUPPORT YOU CAN!
posts.content:
I will write a bit of context here so everyone understands, sorry for the long text, but I owe at least an explanation of the situation.

Sunday was the first round of presidential elections here. The top 2 candidates, if no one has over 50% from the first round, go to the second round. One of those is what you would call ultra-MAGA (just the Romanian version, so...ultra-MRGA?). The other, is an almost perfect carbon copy of Kamala Harris, only that she is white. The second round is on the 8th of December, more on this later.

THE MOST IMPORTANT THING, HOWEVER, ARE THE PARLIAMENTARY ELECTIONS THIS SUNDAY (1ST OF DECEMBER, WHICH IS ROMANIA'S 4TH OF JULY!).

Based parties and political movements have been on the rise and a good score in the parliamentary elections is crucial. In Romania, the Parliament holds much more power than the president. Every extra vote for those parties matters, because every extra percentage means more seats, which translates into more influence. Even if we don;t outright win, we can still stop the woke/globalist parties and perhaps work with the moderates (Romania has a 3rd, more "traditional" political sphere, which I'd say is neither excessively woke, nor conservative). I want us to win, I'll do everything I can to mobilize like-minded people, but every single inch of help is needed.

Then, on the 8th, the 2nd round of presidential elections will take place and it will only be us versus the woke "woman". ALL MAINSTREAM MEDIA IS WORKING OVERTIME TO SMEAR US, INSULT US, DEMINE AND MISLEAD VOTERS, JUST LIKE IT HAPPENED TO TRUMP! No one, NO ONE expected our guy to be 1st in the first round, but the fight has only just started.

I am asking, no, begging you for any kind of support, be it a prayer, high energy. If you see a post about this anywhere, upvote/like/retweet/comment/do whatever you can to boost the engagement. We need this victory as much as you needed Trump to win. The western world needs more winners that will stop the madness and help us back off from the ledge that we are on. We must stop wokeness, but most of all, we need to prevent World War 3.

Thank you very much and godspeed! Congratulations, again, for the great victory you had, we need the same inspiration for our battle, which may seem like our own, but this battle is part of the same war for saving the western world.
